\fB\-\-api\-description\fR <arg> 
Description placed in the API status header, default: cgminer version
.TP
\fB\-\-api\-groups\fR <arg>  
API one letter groups G:cmd:cmd[,P:cmd:*...] defining the cmds a groups can use
