.TP
\fB\-\-api\-port\fR <arg>    
Port number of miner API (default: 4028)
.TP
\fB\-\-balance\fR           
Change multipool strategy from failover to even share balance
.TP
\fB\-\-benchmark\fR         
Run cgminer in benchmark mode \- produces no shares
